creator: Virtuoso Leagues
descriptionHtml:
Tournament V is an app that easily create tournaments for your football sports and gaming e-sports competition. This is a simple app which hosts your tournaments for anyone and everyone.

Well calibrated tournament systems
Customize your tournament by adding a single or multi-stage format. This includes round-robin (leagues, groups) and single-elimination bracket (knockout) types.

Share, spectate and participate in your tournaments
Create multiple teams and add them to your tournament format. Share your tournaments to your audience. Real users can also participate and automatically Join+ a team. Get instant notifications when a real user request to join your tournament. Alternatively, create multiple generic players to add or modify your team rosters.

Flexible match schedule with standings
Automatically generate your fixtures at random or manually enter a participant to each round. Standings are reflected in real time whenever you update the result.

Display key statistics
Important match events that you have added such as goals, assists, yellow cards, red cards, and top players are tabulated with rankings.

If you like these features and more, download now and give it a try for free.

title: Tournament V

creator: Virtuoso Leagues
descriptionHtml:
Tournament V is an app that easily create tournaments for your football sports and gaming e-sports competition. This is a simple app which hosts your tournaments for anyone and everyone.

Key Features:

Well calibrated tournament systems:
Create and manage your tournament in a matter of minutes.
Customizable settings for a single or multi-stage format tournaments including round-robin (leagues, groups), single-elimination and double-elimination bracket.

Engaging Participation:
Create multiple teams and add them to your tournament format.
Share with your audience to spectate or join a team.
Get instant notifications when a real user request to join your tournament.
Create multiple generic players to add or modify your existing team rosters.

Flexible match schedule:
Generate fixtures randomly or manually enter a participant in each round.
Real-time update of scores, brackets, and standings.

Display key statistics:
Tabulate key match events such as goals, assists, cards, and top players.
Set match line-up with appearances and ratings as additional statistics.

Multiple admin tools:
Key admin options available include one tournament admin, team admin, and match admin.

If you like these features and more, download now and give it a try for free.
